title: "US35 — Detailed effect estimates"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Premium User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>AdvancedAnalyticsScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>ComputeEffectEstimates (rule)
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>WorkoutSession · WorkoutType
  A->>B: open effect estimates
  B->>C: compute(range)
  C->>E: listEndedSessions(userId, from: range)
  E-->>C: List (WorkoutSession + WorkoutType)
  note over C: WorkoutType effect rules applied client-side<br/>(rule-based, no AI)
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (short / long-term effects)
  B-->>A: detailed effect breakdown
  note over E: listEndedSessions via WorkoutGateway → Supabase (RLS)
